data.title: Oil Companies and Members
data.meta_description: 165559756 Oil Companies and Members - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains a list of names, titles, and countries for over 100 individuals. It includes representatives from companies in industries such as oil and gas, media, engineering, government, and more. The majority are from countries in the Middle East and North Africa region as well as some European and North American countries.
